{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Talk_in_the_Park",
  "title": "A Talk in the Park",
  "summary": "Beneath a shade tree in Fountain Square in Plaxton City on Caspar, the Jedi Jessalyn and the mechanic Orson spend a lazy afternoon trading affection and daydreams of surfing every beach in the galaxy. The mood shifts when Orson reveals he must return alone to Talon Karrde's base on Myrkr for a big meeting in a few days; Jessalyn, masking her disappointment, urges him to be careful and turns the talk to their stalled effort to heal the mind-damaged Eva Sargent, whose injury she traces to the Sith Valak and fears she cannot undo without Luke Skywalker's help. Orson, quietly protective and a little jealous of her regard for Luke, presses her to look after herself given her own dark history with the Emperor. As the afternoon drifts on, Jessalyn shares warm memories of her childhood home on Yavin -- its roses and old temples -- and the two are joined by Drew, with whom they make idle plans to go surfing before Orson signals it is time, while they are all together, to discuss their next steps.",
